%% --- Placeholder version ---

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as <Client>
    participant Gateway as <Gateway>
    participant Service as <Service>
    participant DataLayer as <DataLayer>
    participant Database as <Database>

    Client->>Gateway: Request
    Gateway->>Service: Forward (authenticated)
    Service->>DataLayer: Query / Command
    DataLayer->>Database: SQL / Driver call
    Database-->>DataLayer: Result set
    DataLayer-->>Service: Domain object
    Service-->>Gateway: Response payload
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTP response

